description: A warped, wooden storage shed bows low to the grass-ridden earth, its feeble walls bent outward as it sags under the now-insufferable load of its plank roof.  A yawning and badly leaning doorway leads into a dark interior.

A warped, wooden storage shed bows low to the grass-ridden earth, its feeble walls bent outward as it sags under the now-insufferable load of its plank roof.  Damaged beyond repair by the alternating forces of sun and rain, the weathered wood of the decrepit structure appears ready to collapse.  A yawning and badly leaning doorway leads into a dark interior.
